subject: NCAA Lacrosse Championships
Lacrosse
lead_paragraph: Attackman Eric Lusby tied a career high with five goals to lead top-seeded Loyola (Md.) to a 10-9 victory over Denver in the N.C.A.A. tournament quarterfinals in Annapolis, Md.
